<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink382">
<l>puḷḷolik kamartta kaṇṇaḷ veḷvēṟ</l>
<l>ṟiruntukaḻaṟ kāḷaiyo ṭaruñcuraṅ kaḻivō</l>
<l>ḷelliṭai yacainta kalleṉ cīṟūrp</l>
<l>puṉaiyiḻai makaḷirp payanta</l>
<l>maṉaikeḻu peṇṭirkku nōvumār peritē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>The girl whose eyes startle at the cries of birds, </l>
<l>passed through the harsh wasteland with her young man  </l>
<l>in perfect anklets and a shining spear, </l>
<l>to bring much suffering to the women from the house, </l>
<l>who have borne daughters [adorned] with fine jewels,</l>
<l>in the small noisy village, which is taking rest at night. </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
